---
import { Mail, MessageCircle, Github } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="px-5 py-24 xl:px-96 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8 animate-slide-in-from-bottom"
>
  <!--Infos -->
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
    <h3 class="text-4xl/10 md:text-5xl/20 font-extrabold">
      Vamos trabalhar <strong
        class="bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-500 via-violet-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >juntos</strong
      >
    </h3>
    <h4 class="text-lg text-neutral-400 mt-2 max-w-xl">
      Tem um projeto em mente? Vamos conversar sobre como posso transformar sua
      visão em realidade. Estou sempre aberto para novas oportunidades e
      colaborações.
    </h4>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-start drop-shadow-[0_0_100px_#615FFF]"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 border border-neutral-700 backdrop-blur-3xl rounded-lg bg-black/30 animate-slide-in-from-left"
      >
        <span class="text-neutral-400"><Mail class="inline" /> Email</span>
        <a href="mailto:henriquehnnm987@gmail.com" class="hover:underline"
          >henriquehnnm987@gmail.com</a
        >
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 border border-neutral-700 backdrop-blur-3xl rounded-lg bg-black/30 animate-slide-in-from-right"
      >
        <span class="text-neutral-400"
          ><MessageCircle class="inline" /> WhatsApp</span
        >
        <a href="tel:+5562992458282" class="hover:underline"
          >+55 (62) 99245-8282</a
        >
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 border border-neutral-700 backdrop-blur-3xl rounded-lg bg-black/30 md:col-span-2 text-left md:text-center animate-slide-in-from-bottom"
      >
        <span class="text-neutral-400"><Github class="inline" /> GitHub</span>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Henriquehnnm"
          target="_blank"
          class="hover:underline">/Henriquehnnm</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
